data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. Spacious Pool home located in East Orlando in the Andover Cay Community!  This 2-story 5 bedroom, 3 bath home offers space and flexibility for multigenerational living.  NEW Pool Enclosure 2021, NEW Pool motor 2022, NEW Water Heater 2022, AC replaced approximately 5 years ago, Roof 2015, Exterior painted 3 years ago, Interior freshly painted last year and so much more.  As you enter the home a welcoming foyer leads to a formal living room, home office perfect for remote work, and the family room at the back of the home.  The family room, dining room and kitchen are the perfect area to entertain with sliding doors leading to the pool and covered lanai.  An island in the kitchen provides a perfect prep space and large windows allow natural light to flood the open spaces.   The dining area features a bay window overlooking the sparkling pool.  A downstairs bedroom is just off the family room with an attached bathroom that also serves as the pool bath with an exterior door to the lanai.  This bedroom also has access through the garage offering a perfect place for long term guests or an in-law suite with private access.  Step outside to enjoy the covered lanai and enjoy the Florida lifestyle in your sparkling pool and herringbone paver patio.  Enjoy the sounds of water flowing over the waterfall.  Your private oasis awaits with a fully fenced backyard and no rear neighbors!  Upstairs you will find the large master suite with NEW laminate flooring, spacious walk-in closets, two sinks, separate shower, and garden tub.  The additional three bedrooms share a hall bathroom.  An additional loft area is the perfect place for a playroom or additional remote workspace.  The options are endless with all of this space!   The community has a private Community pool, Playground and park.  Just minutes to major roadways to get you anywhere in Central Florida.  All of this and just minutes to Waterford Lakes retail and restaurants!  Schedule your private showing today.
